  <th>Anbieter-Beispiel</th>
  <th>Kosten</th>
  <th>Notizen</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
  <td><strong>Training (Llama 3.3 70B auf 10K Samples)</strong></td>
  <td>Together AI</td>
  <td class="number">$300</td>
  <td>LoRA auf einzelner H100 GPU (~4 Stunden)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td><strong>Inferenz (pro 1M Tokens)</strong></td>
  <td>Groq (Llama 3.3 70B)</td>
  <td class="number">$0,27</td>
  <td>Schnell (keine Tuning-Latenz vs Fine-Tuned GPT-4)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td><strong>Inferenz (pro 1M Tokens)</strong></td>
  <td>Together AI (Llama 3.3 70B)</td>
  <td class="number">$0,18</td>
